{"tid":2302251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐西蘭國會議員 James McDowall MP用廣東話於國會宣誓","createTime":"2020-11-27T03:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T12:40:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":102,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"50ca2db8462f95ff0667d05982a2f832d87ee3b0","tid":2302251,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DrMcDowallACT/videos/811338222768359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDrMcDowallACT%2Fvideos%2F811338222768359&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=93efc13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DrMcDowallACT/videos/811338222768359</a><br />\n<br />\nCommission Opening of Parliament<br />\n<br />\nThe swearing in of Members of Parliament at the Comission Opening occured earlier today. Members have the option of stating their oath in two languages if they wish, and as a nod to the other half of my family I repeated mine in Cantonese.<br />\n<br />\nI, James Samuel McDowall, swear that I will be faithful and bear true allegiance to Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth the Second, Her heirs and successors, according to law. So help me God.<br />\n<br />\n本人James Samuel McDowall，真誠發誓，定當依據法律，對女皇陛下伊麗莎白二世，及其繼承及繼位人效忠，並會盡忠職守。願上帝助我"},{"pid":"14f9a29b5de2e1a598ae47e51bf586cbec26dbb9","tid":2302251,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381bf1e908d6f7141729513321e7a83548673f40","tid":2302251,"uid":91205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa